I had tears in my eyes at the line 
"Saanu Sauda nhi pugda, 
Raavi ton Chanaab puchhda ki haal hai Satluj da".
The meaning of this line is Chenab River (on the border) asks Raavi (in Pak) how's Satluj (in India)? Like a friend separated from the other!

snippet.textDisplay: Scars of partition still haunt humanity. But isn't it amusing that after so many years of carnage and massacre in Punjab both sides are romanticizing the other side as if no one wrecked havoc upon the opposing communities in Punjab in 47. We are fools and keep fooling ourselves. We know communal fault line brought mass scale destruction in Punjab and Punjab was divided without taking counts of the sensitivities in various districts. Like those in gurdaspur, jalandhar from where my grandparents came from, ludhiana, amritsar. These districts struck with worst of killings and humanity lost sanity.
